snippet.title: Nautapa 2025 On Monsoon | नौतपा क्या होता है और इसका मॉनसून से क्या है संबंध । Kisan India
snippet.description:
नौतपा 2025 को लेकर मौसम में आया अनोखा बदलाव! इस साल नौतपा के दौरान गर्मी का तेज असर कम देखने को मिला, जिससे अब मॉनसून के पैटर्न में भी बदलाव की संभावना जताई जा रही है।
इस वीडियो में जानिए:
नौतपा क्या होता है और इसका मॉनसून से क्या संबंध है?
Kisan India खेती-किसानी से जुड़ी हर महत्वपूर्ण जानकारी प्रदान करता है। यहां आपको नवीनतम कृषि तकनीक, सरकारी योजनाएं, बाजार भाव, विशेषज्ञ सलाह और बहुत कुछ मिलेगा। हमारे साथ जुड़कर आप खेती से संबंधित सभी जरूरी खबरें, अपडेट्स और टिप्स पा सकते हैं। खेती को और भी लाभकारी बनाने के लिए हमारे वीडियो को जरूर देखें!
#Nautapa2025 #Monsoon2025 #WeatherAlert #MausamUpdate #IMDNews
#KisanIndia #KisanIndiaOfficial #KisanIndiaNews #AgriNews

snippet.title: MVP OR WHAT | JONATHAN IS BACK!! | BGMI!
snippet.description:
Hey Guys, I’m Jonathan Amaral, better known as Jonathan Gaming, a professional BGMI esports athlete and streamer.

Since the start of my journey, my dedication to the game has been defined by precision, consistency, and an unstoppable grind. As an assaulter, I’ve built a reputation for clutch performances and high-impact gameplay, earning respect in the BGMI community. 

Through years of dedication, I’ve honed my skills, adapting to every challenge and evolving with the game. Whether in high-stakes tournaments or streaming for the gaming community, my focus remains the same - pushing the limits and delivering top-tier gameplay.

Redbull Athlete 🧢
BGIS 2025 Runner up 🥈
BGIS 2025 Finals MVP 👑
BGIS 2025 Overall Top Fragger 🎯
BMPS 2024 2nd Runner up 🥉
BGMS 2022 MVP 🏆
BGMS 2022 Runner up 🥈
BGIS 2021 Overall Top Fragger 🎯
PMWL #2 Overall Fragger 💣
PMCO Globals #4 Fragger 💣
PMPL 2020 Finals #2 Fragger 🎯
PMPL 2020 Finals Runner up 🥈
PMIS 2020 Top Fragger 🎯
PMIS 2020 India Champions 🏆
PMCO 2019 Fall Split SA Champion 🏆

Lyrics:

Sise ki meri jawani
Mai hu pari Aasmani
Aankhe Gulabi Gulabi
Masti bhari jindagani 

Lakho diwana Mare Rojana 
Dil Hola Bekarar 
Aaela Jab Chal Ke 

Karela Bawal Tohar Ghaghara Jalidar 
Dupatta Mal Mal Ke

Ho Jaye Da Pyar 
Kahe Karelu Inkar 
Jawani Jhal Jhal Jhalke 

Na A Dada E Na Hoi
De Deba Tu Dhokha Dhoka

Dhakate Dhakan Hamar 80 Ke Raftar 
Kabo Halke Halke

Karela Bawal Tohar Ghaghara Jalidar 
Dupatta Mal Mal Ke

Aag Lage style Par 
Hola Murder Smile Par 

Najariya Far Far Farake
Mohabat Ba Bhar Bhar Ke

Karejawa Dhak Dhak Dhadke
Odhaniya Sar Sarke

Dekhela Tab Tab 
Penhila Jab Jab 
Hathawa Me Chatkar 
Chudi Lalke Lalke

Gora Gora Face Pa 
Gori Kala Kala Bal 
Lipistik Purple Ke

Dhakate Dil E Hamar 
80 Ke Raftar 
Kabo Halke Halke

Chauraha Kabo Gali pa
Aawe Bhaura eh Kali Pa

Umariya Nanhki Nanhki
Satelu Tanki Tanki 
Marat Balu Kankhi Kankhi 
Ta Manawa Sanaki Sanki 

Sahal Na Jala nahi Sohala 
Hamara Ke Bewahar Aashu Neelkamal Ke 

Jab Se Tohake Dekhale Bani 
Chadhata Bukhar 
Jarurat Ba Phal Ke 

Karela Bawal Tohar Ghaghara Jalidar 
Dupatta Mal Mal Ke

snippet.title: Driver के बारे में जानकर Jetha क्यों हुआ Shock? | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Jetha Jasoos
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to the Sony LIV Channel: 
https://www.youtube.com/user/sonyliv

Everyone argues over the unaddressed tempo in the Gokuldham Society. Bapuji intervenes and asks them to come up with a solution rather than arguing with each other. Jethalal has a heartfelt conversation with his grandfather. Later, he revisits memories of the Republic Day celebration and decides to call Babitaji to appreciate Mahila Mandal's efforts for the preparations. Jethalal reads the letter to Babitaji that she found in Iyer's book. It was a love letter that he translates completely for Babitaji. Later, Jethalal's fear comes true, when Sundar arrives at his home and starts dancing.

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sonyliv #comedy #comedy2025 #jethalal #jethalalcomedy #tmkoc #taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah 

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The residents of the housing society, help each other find solutions when they face common, real-life challenges and get involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch episodes from 'Jetha Jasoos' : https://www.youtube.com/playlist?
list=PLn5vww_8o5Ku3tHY5oVV9jcxOqy9fOVW7

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 4408 | 27 May 2025 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 4408: Investment Ki Chinta

snippet.title: वट सावित्री पूजा 2025 - Savitri Mata Aarti - जय सावित्री माता | Vat Savitri Aarti | Vat Saviti 2025
snippet.description:
वट सावित्री पूजा 2025 - Savitri Mata Aarti - जय सावित्री माता | Vat Savitri Aarti | Vat Saviti 2025 - सावित्री माता जी की आरती

ज्येष्ठ माह सुहागिन महिलाओं के लिए अधिक महत्वपूर्ण होता है। इसका कारण है वट सावित्री व्रत। दरअसल, ज्येष्ठ मास की अमावस्या तिथि पर वट सावित्री का पर्व मनाया जाता है। इस दिन महिलाएं पति की लंबी उम्र व तरक्की के लिए निर्जला व्रत रखती हैं। मान्यता है कि इस दिन देवी सावित्री ने यमराज से पति सत्यवान के प्राण वापिस ले लिए थे। इस पर्व में मुख्य रूप से वट वृक्ष की पूजा की जाती है। कहा जाता है कि इस पेड़ में ब्रह्मा, विष्णु और शिव जी का वास होता है। इसलिए इसकी उपासना करने से तीनों देवताओं का आशीर्वाद प्राप्त होता है।

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 4408 - Maya Jaal Me Phase Gokuldhamwasi?! | Taarak Mehta ka Ooltah Chashmah
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Step into Jethalal’s world with Gada Electronics!  Manage the shop, tackle quirky customers, and experience nonstop TMKOC-style fun. 

Are you ready for the challenge? 
Play now: https://gadaelectronics.page.link/dhgB  
#GadaElectronics #TMKOCGame

Watch the FULL MOVIE of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSk2_rPKNCDcjNAA8vaDN-E&si=rC5AotwLD2r3MHna

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Jheel Mehta / Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani / Khushi Mali as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal / Monaz Mevawalla as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah / Dharmit Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku 
Ghanshyam Nayak / Kiran Bhatt as Nattu Kaka

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: हंपीतल्या आजीचं जेवण | जगातील सर्वात चवदार पदार्थ | Traditional Food | Village cooking
snippet.description:
कर्नाटक मधल्या आजीचं हंपीच जेवण माझ्या आयुष्यातील सर्वात चवदार जेवण . जेवण साधं सोपं गावाकडचंच होत पण त्याला एक मायेची चव होती . 
 हंपी मध्ये एक ६०-७० वर्ष्याची आजी तिच्या लाकडी बुट्टीमधे २०- ३० कडक भाकरी घेऊन बसलेली होती त्यासोबत लाल मिरचीचा खर्डा , शेंगदाण्याची चटणी , मुगाची उसळ आणि थंडगार ताकाचा ग्लास , दही होते ते जेवण बघून खाण्याची इच्छा झाली जेवण काही महाग नव्हतं पण चव मात्र खूपच छान होती आज असंच जेवण करणार आहे , पण आजीच्या हातासारखी काय चव येणार नाही , धन्यवाद . 
हंपीतल्या आजीचं जगातलं सगळ्यात चवदार जेवण 

मसाला ऑर्डर करण्यासाठी या नंबर वरती whatsup करा  - 8830473030

Foods that are rich in tradition and high on health — that is what you get in villages across India. 
Here's a glimpse into the wonderful flavors and tastes that make up our culinary heritage.

About YRF Spy Universe:
YRF Spy Universe is a first of its kind cinematic universe of spy thriller films in India. The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger", starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War" was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. "Pathaan" was the fourth instalment in the Spy Universe franchise which was released in 2023 starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham. "Tiger 3", the fifth instalment in the YRF Spy Universe and the third film in the Tiger series, starring Salman Khan, Katrina Kaif and Emraan Hashmi, released in 2023. "War 2" is the sixth film of the YRF Spy Universe franchise and will release on 14 August 2025. The film stars two of the greatest cinematic icons Hrithik Roshan and NTR, with Kiara Advani in the lead and is directed by Ayan Mukerji. “Alpha”, the seventh instalment in the franchise and Hindi cinema's first female-led YRF Spy Universe film, starring Alia Bhatt and Sharvari, is set to release on 25 December 2025.

"Pathaan" was the fourth instalment in the Spy Universe franchise which was released in 2023 starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham. "Tiger 3", the fifth instalment in the YRF Spy Universe and the third film in the Tiger series, starring Salman Khan, Katrina Kaif and Emraan Hashmi, released in 2023. "War 2" is the sixth film of the YRF Spy Universe franchise and will release on 14 August 2025. The film stars two of the greatest cinematic icons Hrithik Roshan and NTR, with Kiara Advani in the lead and is directed by Ayan Mukerji. “Alpha”, the seventh instalment in the franchise and Hindi cinema's first female-led YRF Spy Universe film, starring Alia Bhatt and Sharvari, is set to release on 25 December 2025.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: FRUIT MIXER | Colorful Healthy Fruits Mixed Recipe | Summer Health Fruit Recipe Making in Village
snippet.description:
Today in our village, we made a colorful and healthy fruit mixer using fresh fruits. We included apples, oranges, watermelon, strawberries, kiwis, mangoes, papayas, jackfruit, and more, along with soaked almond gum, basil seeds, and pure honey for added taste and health benefits.

The video beautifully cuts and shows all the fruits, making it refreshing and satisfying to watch. This natural recipe is perfect for all seasons, especially summer, and is a great healthy fruit recipe for kids.

it.title: Mix di frutta | Ricetta per un mix di frutta sana e colorata | Ricetta per un mix di frutta sana ...
it.description:
Oggi nel nostro villaggio abbiamo preparato un frullato di frutta colorato e sano usando frutta fresca. Abbiamo aggiunto mele, arance, anguria, fragole, kiwi, mango, papaya, jackfruit e altro ancora, insieme a gomma di mandorle in ammollo, semi di basilico e miele puro per un gusto ancora più intenso e benefici per la salute.

Il video mostra e taglia splendidamente tutti i frutti, rendendolo rinfrescante e appagante da guardare. Questa ricetta naturale è perfetta per tutte le stagioni, soprattutto d'estate, ed è un'ottima ricetta di frutta sana per i bambini.

fr-FR.title: MÉLANGEUR DE FRUITS | Recette de mélange de fruits sains et colorés | Recette de fruits sains pou...
fr-FR.description:
Aujourd'hui, dans notre village, nous avons préparé un mixeur de fruits coloré et sain avec des fruits frais. Nous avons utilisé des pommes, des oranges, de la pastèque, des fraises, des kiwis, des mangues, des papayes, du jacquier et bien d'autres ingrédients, ainsi que de la gomme d'amande imbibée, des graines de basilic et du miel pur pour plus de goût et de bienfaits pour la santé.

La vidéo présente tous les fruits avec élégance, ce qui la rend rafraîchissante et agréable à regarder. Cette recette naturelle est parfaite en toutes saisons, surtout en été, et constitue une excellente recette de fruits saine pour les enfants.

es-US.title: MEZCLADOR DE FRUTAS | Receta de frutas variadas, coloridas y saludables | Receta de frutas saluda...
es-US.description:
Hoy en nuestro pueblo, preparamos una colorida y saludable mezcla de frutas frescas. Incluimos manzanas, naranjas, sandía, fresas, kiwis, mangos, papayas, yaca y más, además de goma de almendras remojada, semillas de albahaca y miel pura para darle más sabor y beneficios para la salud.

El video muestra todas las frutas con una cuidada selección, lo que lo hace refrescante y satisfactorio. Esta receta natural es perfecta para todas las estaciones, especialmente el verano, y es una excelente receta de frutas saludables para niños.

de-DE.title: FRUCHTMIXER | Rezept für bunte, gesunde Früchte | Sommerliches, gesundes Obstrezept im Dorf zuber...
de-DE.description:
Heute haben wir in unserem Dorf einen farbenfrohen und gesunden Fruchtmixer mit frischen Früchten zubereitet. Wir haben Äpfel, Orangen, Wassermelonen, Erdbeeren, Kiwis, Mangos, Papayas, Jackfrüchte und mehr verwendet, zusammen mit eingeweichtem Mandelkernmehl, Basilikumsamen und reinem Honig für zusätzlichen Geschmack und gesunde Vorteile.

Das Video zeigt alle Früchte mit schönen Schnitten und ist erfrischend und unterhaltsam anzusehen. Dieses natürliche Rezept eignet sich perfekt für jede Jahreszeit, besonders für den Sommer, und ist ein tolles, gesundes Obstrezept für Kinder.

pt-BR.title: MIXER DE FRUTAS | Receita de Frutas Coloridas e Saudáveis ​​| Receita de Frutas Saudáveis ​​para ...
pt-BR.description:
Hoje, em nossa aldeia, fizemos uma mistura de frutas colorida e saudável usando frutas frescas. Incluímos maçãs, laranjas, melancia, morangos, kiwis, mangas, mamões, jacas e muito mais, além de goma de amêndoa demolhada, sementes de manjericão e mel puro para adicionar sabor e benefícios à saúde.

O vídeo corta e mostra todas as frutas com perfeição, tornando-o refrescante e prazeroso de assistir. Esta receita natural é perfeita para todas as estações, especialmente o verão, e é uma ótima receita de frutas saudáveis ​​para crianças.

hi.title: फल मिक्सर | रंग-बिरंगे स्वस्थ फल मिश्रित रेसिपी | गांव में गर्मियों में स्वास्थ्यवर्धक फल रेसिपी ...
hi.description:
आज हमारे गांव में, हमने ताजे फलों का उपयोग करके एक रंगीन और स्वस्थ फल मिक्सर बनाया। हमने सेब, संतरे, तरबूज, स्ट्रॉबेरी, कीवी, आम, पपीता, कटहल, और बहुत कुछ शामिल किया, साथ ही स्वाद और स्वास्थ्य लाभ के लिए भिगोए हुए बादाम गोंद, तुलसी के बीज और शुद्ध शहद भी मिलाया।

वीडियो में सभी फलों को खूबसूरती से काटा और दिखाया गया है, जिससे इसे देखना ताज़ा और संतोषजनक लगता है। यह प्राकृतिक नुस्खा सभी मौसमों, खासकर गर्मियों के लिए एकदम सही है, और बच्चों के लिए एक बढ़िया स्वस्थ फल नुस्खा है।

id.title: FRUIT MIXER | Resep Campuran Buah Sehat Berwarna-warni | Resep Buah Sehat Musim Panas yang Dibuat...
id.description:
Hari ini di desa kami, kami membuat campuran buah yang berwarna-warni dan sehat menggunakan buah-buahan segar. Kami memasukkan apel, jeruk, semangka, stroberi, kiwi, mangga, pepaya, nangka, dan banyak lagi, bersama dengan getah almond yang direndam, biji kemangi, dan madu murni untuk menambah rasa dan manfaat kesehatan.

Video ini memotong dan menunjukkan semua buah dengan indah, sehingga menyegarkan dan memuaskan untuk ditonton. Resep alami ini cocok untuk semua musim, terutama musim panas, dan merupakan resep buah sehat yang bagus untuk anak-anak.

ja.title: フルーツミキサー | カラフルでヘルシーなフルーツミックスレシピ | 村で作る夏のヘルシーフルーツレシピ
ja.description:
今日は村で、新鮮なフルーツを使ってカラフルでヘルシーなフルーツミキサーを作りました。リンゴ、オレンジ、スイカ、イチゴ、キウイ、マンゴー、パパイヤ、ジャックフルーツなど、様々なフルーツに加え、風味と健康効果を高めるために、アーモンドガム、バジルシード、そして純粋なハチミツを加えました。

この動画では、様々なフルーツが美しくカットされ、その姿が映し出されているので、見ているだけで爽快で満足感があります。このナチュラルなレシピは、特に夏など、どの季節にもぴったりで、お子様にもぴったりのヘルシーなフルーツレシピです。

Directed by: Mani Ratnam

Lyrics:
Enna venum unakku  
Kotti kotti kidakku  
Innum enna venum unakku  
Sorgam ingu irukku  

Kallam ulle nenju  
Kadhalendra nanju  
Kannai moodi kondu  
Ennai mattum konju  

Enna venum unakku  
Kotti kotti kidakku  
Innum enna venum unakku  
Sorgam ingu irukku  

Sugar baby en  
Sugar baby  
Sugar baby en  
Sugar baby (2)  

Anaikka vaa  
Anaikka vaa (2)  

Enna venum unakku  
Kotti kotti kidakku  
Innum enna venum unakku  
Sorgam ingu irukku  

Kaliyugam idhu  
Kadal eriyudhu  
Pagai nerunguthu  
Padai konduva.. va  

Varuguthu Puli  
Vilaguthu Nadhi  
Adi Athiradi  
Edhirigal Bali  

Vaal. Neelam Vedham Odhudhu  
Veesum Kaathule Vesham Maaruthu  
Indha Pollatha Ooru VeNaamadi  
Ni Vanthaal Sari..  
En Ulage Neeyadi..

If love is a crime, my baby is criminal. 
criminal criminal criminal criminal. 
I pay the fine to the time, 
without mining him cynical. 
cynical cynical cynical. 
If being rich is a sin, 
I wanna be a sinner sinner sinner sinner. 
Now I am married to the game
 I am gonna be the winner winner winner winner.

Innum enna venum unakku  
Sorgam ingu irukku

snippet.title: The mind of a Genius: Kamal Haasan on Art, life and passion | Gobinath
snippet.description:
Enquiries:
talk2gobinath@gmail.com

#Gobinath #kamalhaasan #ulaganayagan #art #life #passion #legacy #podcast #cinema #tamilcinema #legacyofexcellence 

Stay ahead with direct updates from Gobinath — interviews, insights, and powerful voices.
Join the official WhatsApp Channel today:
https://whatsapp.com/channel/0029Vb5gNn82Jl8DSfwhUM3G

In this powerful episode, Gobinath sits down with the legendary Ulaganayagan Kamal Haasan—a visionary who has not just acted in cinema but revolutionized it. 

With fearless creativity, deep philosophy, and decades of reinvention, Kamal reflects on a life lived in service of art. From listening to the heart over algorithms to exploring aging, AI, acting, and mortality, this conversation dives into the mind of a master.

From listening to the heart over algorithms to exploring aging, AI, and the ethics of cinema, Kamal opens up about:

 • His constant reinvention and evolution as an artist
 • The humbling moments that shaped his self-awareness
 • Learning from the ancients, yet daring to innovate
 • Acting not as imitation but as raw, requested “misbehavior”
 • Balancing perfection with beautiful imperfection
 • Time, discipline, mortality—and the pursuit of artistic immortality
 • The philosophies behind his cinema: for whom, and why
 • The tension between market demands and meaningful messaging
 • Minimalism, nostalgia, and the emotional universality of war and motherhood
 • His Gandhian turn and his deeply underrated contributions as a lyricist
 • Tamil’s rhythmic beauty and its global poetic power
 • The role of cinema in shaping society and the next generation
 • Corporate capitalism, global politics, and center-aligned balance
 • Parenting, emotional intelligence, and legacy beyond screens
 • His take on AI, knowledge, and the evolving boundaries of intelligence
 • The behind-the-scenes genius of the technicians behind Thug Life
 • And his reflections on the title Thug Life and its connection to Nayakan

Kamal also shares heartfelt memories from his childhood, honors icons like Sivaji, Kannadasan, Periyar, and Kalaignar, and lays bare what continues to drive his tireless journey as a creator.

This episode is more than an interview—it’s a philosophical masterclass, a celebration of art, and a tribute to the spirit of relentless curiosity.

A must-watch for cinephiles, thinkers, artists, and dreamers who believe in the power of storytelling to change the world.

snippet.description:
Housefull 5 Trailer Review By Deeksha Sharma. Akshay Kumar Comeback in Comedy with Housefull 5 Franchise is all set for Box Office Surprise after Mystery Thriller Twist & Turns in a Family Comedy Cinema. Housefull 5 Trailer is big on Jokes but Short on Suspense supported by a Larger than life Supporting Cast.

Starring :  
Akshay Kumar, Abhishek A Bachchan, Riteish Deshmukh, Jacqueline Fernandez, Sonam Bajwa, Nargis Fakhri, Sanjay Dutt, Jackie Shroff, Nana Patekar, Chitrangada Singh, Fardeen Khan, Chunky Pandey, Johnny Lever, Shreyas Talpade, Dino Morea, Ranjeet, Soundarya Sharma, Nikitin Dheer, and Akashdeep Sabir

snippet.title: Bhide aur Jethalal ki Ladai! | FULL MOVIE | Part 1 | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Watch the FULL MOVIE of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSk2_rPKNCDcjNAA8vaDN-E&si=rC5AotwLD2r3MHna

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Jheel Mehta / Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani / Khushi Mali as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal / Monaz Mevawalla as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah / Dharmit Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku 
Ghanshyam Nayak / Kiran Bhatt as Nattu Kaka
Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha
Navina Wadekar / Monika Bhadoriya as Bawri

Produced By: Neela Asit Modi, Asit Kumarr Modi 
Special Thanks: Mahesh Vakil, Indu Tarak Mehta

The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

🎵 Spotify: https://open.spotify.com/track/4svHgHyAhvhTM5WblTKFmZ?si=7a302fc003f94b86
🍏 Apple Music: https://music.apple.com/us/song/2-gulaab-returns/1814334468
🎼 iTunes: https://music.apple.com/us/song/2-gulaab-returns/1814334468
🔊 Amazon Prime Music: https://music.amazon.in/tracks/B0F8NLYKK9?marketplaceId=A21TJRUUN4KGV&musicTerritory=IN&ref=dm_sh_8YrKq8xtznX0UkoBW8813qab2
🎧 YouTube Music: https://music.youtube.com/watch?v=e-pe54Zoz5c&si=2PYKr-B7Z5ONW0JW
🎶 JioSaavn: https://www.jiosaavn.com/song/2-gulaab-returns/BQ1TCRZvaEY
🎧 Gaana: https://gaana.com/song/2-gulaab-returns-1


👁️‍🗨️ Lyrics :
Chori bhul te na gayi re purane yaar ne
Ek tarfa thi thai andhi mere pyar ne
Gediyan pe gedi maari saans na liya
Chora aya tha milan kade laal car mein
Ankhya mein leke ghane khaab aya su
Teri khatir main chori re gulab laya su
Aaj bhi yo chaale se pasand teri gel
Mere fool ke liye main poora baag laya su
Billa sonipat aala fir zid pe adeya
Leke lamborghini tere gate pe khada
Mere pache dekh madama ki line laagri
Chora dheeth hai sire ka tere pache padeya
Balka ne aape main khilaya karunga
Sir godi ke mein dharke swaya karunga
Faag aur samman ki lehar dekhiye
Tere naye naye suit chori lyaya karunga

Ashiqui mein saang sikhya rog laag gya
Ranjha hogya jogi mere jog laag gya
Fooli na smaari tu bhi firey nikhri
Pyar ka asar tere hon laag gya
Moti lyau kaadh ke samundra mein ke
Re tu gajab ki cheej saari sundra mein ke
Manne pooje sare chori re faqeer ke re peer
Teri mangu fariyaad sare mandira mein ke
Chand taare tod teri jholi mein bharu
Teri na ho jisme vo kaam na karu
Chora tanne apni re jaan maanrey
Teri aai hove aur pehla mein maru
Fulkariyan ne kheta mein udati chaliye
Geet sonipat aale ke tu gaati chaliye
Visa lagwa ke baat diye sare gaam mein
Team all good aale dhool thate aaliye
Bhola baba dekh chore ki support mein khadeya
Jabe teri gelya ban teri jott mein khadeya
Meri kare rakhwali parchai vo meri
Vo aape dekh sab main te ott mein khadeya
